description:
Tia Mowry [Sister, Sister, The Hot Chick, The Game, Instant Mom] talks with Anna about attending The Hot Chick cheerleading-camp, the formative experience of Sister, Sister, Angelina Jolie, The Goonies, being a twin, collecting crystals, heartbreak, empathy, Dealbreakers and more. Later in the episode, Anna and April offer some qualified and unqualified advice to a caller trying to start a new life and find the right partner.
